            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "he went up into a mountain; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and sitting down, after the manner of the Jewish doctors to show their authority, which our Saviour also at other times observed, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Matthew 26:55 Luke 4:20 John 8:2",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Matthew 26:55",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Luke 4:20",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "John 8:2",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "his disciples came unto him; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " both those strictly so called, and others also, viz. the multitude, mentioned in the last chapter, or some of them; and he began to speak to them with freedom, so as the multitude might hear. Christ thought it as lawful to preach in the mountain as in the synagogues; nor did his disciples doubt the lawfulness of hearing him, wherever he thought fit to speak. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And he opened his mouth,.... He spoke with a clear and strong voice, that all the people might hear him; and with great freedom, utterance, and cheerfulness, and things of the greatest moment and importance; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and taught them; not his disciples only, but the whole multitude, who heard him with astonishment; see Matthew 7:28. Some things in the following discourse are directed to the disciples in particular, and others regard the multitude in general. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and taught them; not his disciples only, but the whole multitude, who heard him with astonishment; see ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Matthew 7:28",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". Some things in the following discourse are directed to the disciples in particular, and others regard the multitude in general. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
